@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:5000

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Ingest AI Result (used by stream_main.py sender)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/result
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timestamp": "2026-03-26T17:30:00",
  "person_count": 3,
  "students": [
    {
      "track_id": 1,
      "name": "SOMCHAI JAIDEE",
      "state": "ตั้งใจเรียน",
      "confirmed": true,
      "confidence": 98.1
    },
    {
      "track_id": 2,
      "name": "SUDAPORN DEEDEE",
      "state": "หลับ/เหม่อ",
      "confirmed": true,
      "confidence": 92.4
    },
    {
      "track_id": 3,
      "name": "คนแปลกหน้า",
      "state": "ฟุบหลับ/หันหลัง",
      "confirmed": false,
      "confidence": 0.0
    }
  ]
}

### Auto-save attendance (manual trigger)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/auto-save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "SOMCHAI JAIDEE",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-26T17:30:00",
  "confidence": 97.2,
  "track_id": 11
}

### List students
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/students?limit=200

### Today report (example: today drowsy count)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/today

### Behavior report by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/behavior?start_date=2026-03-26&end_date=2026-03-26
